# 📊 Flipkart Sales Performance Dashboard

This project showcases a **Flipkart Sales Performance Dashboard** built using **Power BI**.  
The dashboard provides key insights into sales performance across different payment methods, product categories, and customer ratings.

---

## 🚀 Features of the Dashboard
- **KPI Cards**
  - ✅ Total Sales: 10M  
  - ✅ Average Sales: 10K  
  - ✅ Average Rating: 3.02  
  - ✅ Quantity Sold: 4924  

- **Payment Method Analysis**
  - COD: 21.81%  
  - Credit Card: 19.12%  
  - Debit Card: 22.59%  
  - Net Banking: 17.33%  
  - UPI: 19.15%  

- **Product Category Insights**
  - Grocery leads with **819 units sold**  
  - Electronics, Fashion, Toys & Baby, Home Decor, Books, Beauty & Health follow closely  

- **Interactive Filters**
  - Filter data by **Payment Method**  
  - Filter sales trends by **Year**

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- **Power BI** → Data modeling, DAX calculations, dashboard design  
- **Excel** → Data source  

---

## 🎯 Key Learnings
- Built KPI cards to highlight sales performance  
- Used pie charts & bar charts for clear data visualization  
- Designed navigation with buttons (Home, Detail, Page 3)  
- Implemented interactive slicers for dynamic filtering  

